---
title: Shredded Carrot Satay Salad with bulgur, spinach and toasted sesame seeds
description: There are so many appealing elements to this dish it's hard to choose the best thing about it. That's probably because the rich and creamy satay dressing brings out the very best in each individual ingredient.
